Task
Grade GPA
Write a function average that takes an array of marks (an array of student marks) as an argument and returns the grade point average. Round the result to 1 decimal place and return it as a string.
Example:
• the average function ([4, 5, 4, 5]) must return "4.5".
• the average function ([5, 3]) must return "4.0".

Solution
function average (marks) {
 let arr = marks;
     let sum = 0;
       for (let i = 0; i <arr.length; i ++) {
       sum + = arr [i];
       }
   let res = sum / arr.length;
   return res.toFixed (1);
   }
